text: Daniel Skalický (born February 5, 1991) is a Czech professional ice hockey player. He is currently playing for HC Bílí Tygři Liberec of the Czech Extraliga. Skalický made his Czech Extraliga debut playing with HC Bílí Tygři Liberec during the 2009-10 Czech Extraliga season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:HC Bílí Tygři Liberec players Category:Czech ice hockey forwards Category:Sportspeople from Liberec
